{"tid":1778642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【要人】二百萬三罷全港擺街站，十八區要人！要人！","createTime":"2019-12-11T05:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T17:25:49.000Z","uid":221035,"like":53,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"aab9dd2b3b27c4f9d08d21673b72c40f5e0a82ad","tid":1778642,"uid":221035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:53:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">二百萬三罷十八區要人</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zFqiuy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzFqiuy0.jpg&h=2d559e79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n‼️‼️二百萬三罷要人‼️‼️<br />\n嚟緊二百萬三罷將會係全港各區擺街站，宣傳新工會，需要大量人手！<br />\n我哋招募義工幫手擺街站同做地區宣傳！<br />\n不論你係學生、打工仔、有無街站經驗我哋都十分歡迎～<br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以填以下嘅google form<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/dDnx8kytQqKrqhHr9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FdDnx8kytQqKrqhHr9&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=75e5ef28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/dDnx8kytQqKrqhHr9</a><br />\n<br />\n收集資料之後，我哋會再決定街站嘅數目同地點，並且會有專人聯絡各義工<br />\n<br />\n----<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=092a901b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n各行業總Group list <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F478&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=96c894a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/478</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=2c9a334b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"h